 and--frankly--lots of them stink.  lala.com carries &lt;a href="http://www.lala.com/#artist/Drop_Trio"&gt;Drop Trio&lt;/a&gt; *and* their interface doesn't suck.  Interestingly, $.10 gets you indefinite streaming rights to a track.  $.89 get you a DRM-free MP3.  Incredible savings! (Bring your kids.  We have hot dogs.  Those like those, right?)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.lala.com/#artist/Drop_Trio"&gt;Drop Trio on lala.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5783643-7349455936121142025?l=www.droptrio.com%2Fblog' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.droptrio.com/blog/2009/11/lalacom-drop-trio-in-cloud.html</link><author>gerald.patrick.flanagan@gmail.com (Patrick Flanagan)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5783643.post-5777630535749136611</guid><pubDate>Sat, 19 Sep 2009 02:30:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-09-18T21:43:23.630-05:00</atom:updated><title>Black Joe Varley</title><description>&lt;a onblur="try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}" href="http://www.droptrio.com/blog/uploaded_images/1.bjl-742790.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="float:left; margin:0 10px 10px 0;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 200px; height: 137px;" src="http://www.droptrio.com/blog/uploaded_images/1.bjl-742788.jpg" border="0" alt="" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Monday, September 21 Ian will be on the &lt;a href="http://www.cbs.com/late_late_show/"&gt;Late Late Show with Craig Ferguson&lt;/a&gt;. He'll be playing with &lt;a href="http://www.blackjoelewis.com/"&gt;Black Joe Lewis &amp; The Honey Bears&lt;/a&gt;. I think that we can all agree that the world will be a better place when late night tv is exposed to one of Ian's &lt;a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Pk79uCc3xok"&gt;signature keytar solos&lt;/a&gt;. Tune in and see if world peace can finally be a reality.&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5783643-5777630535749136611?l=www.droptrio.com%2Fblog' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.droptrio.com/blog/2009/09/black-joe-varley.html</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (nuje)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5783643.post-7696574406538045184</guid><pubDate>Sat, 12 Sep 2009 00:28:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-09-12T10:00:25.506-05:00</atom:updated><title>Licensed through Magnatune</title><description>Rumor has it that furniture sales in Houston hit record numbers over Labor Day weekend.  Check out the television commercial created by &lt;a href="http://www.youtube.com/user/jrepp629"&gt;Jake Repp&lt;/a&gt; and Judd Meyers that aired in the Houston market over the holiday:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;object height="340" width="560"&gt;&lt;param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/0xNwBk9vwqs&amp;amp;hl=en&amp;amp;fs=1&amp;amp;"&gt;&lt;param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"&gt;&lt;param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"&gt;&lt;embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/0xNwBk9vwqs&amp;amp;hl=en&amp;amp;fs=1&amp;amp;" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true" height="340" width="560"&gt;&lt;/embed&gt;&lt;/object&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5783643-7696574406538045184?l=www.droptrio.com%2Fblog' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.droptrio.com/blog/2009/09/licensed-through-magnatune.html</link><author>gerald.patrick.flanagan@gmail.com (Patrick Flanagan)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5783643.post-9078376432209597862</guid><pubDate>Sat, 29 Aug 2009 19:43:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-08-30T16:37:43.097-05:00</atom:updated><title>Feels Like HRstrut</title><description>Saturday, September 5 I'll be playing at Fitzgerald's with &lt;a href="http://hrstrut.com/"&gt;HRstrut&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;This is a CD release show for the band's third album "Feels Like Flight." The new album is already available for download on iTunes, Amazon, Target etc. and physical copies will be available at the show.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;HRstrut is a modern rock band with thoughtful lyrics and catchy riffs. You can hear a complete tune on the music page of my &lt;a href="http://www.nujemusic.com/"&gt;website&lt;/a&gt;. It's been nearly a decade since the band played its last show, so don't miss this one.&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5783643-9078376432209597862?l=www.droptrio.com%2Fblog' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.droptrio.com/blog/2009/08/feels-like-hrstrut.html</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (nuje)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5783643.post-5128507873901306369</guid><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2009 18:10:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-04-17T13:15:30.045-05:00</atom:updated><title>May 1 @ AvantGarden</title><description>Hey kids - we've got a show coming up on May 1st at AvantGarden in Houston. Check it:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;width: 400px; height: 618px;" src="http://www.droptrio.com/Showdates/avantgarden_2009-05-01_small.jpg" border="0" alt="" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We'll be playing with Austin-based jazzers &lt;a href="http://www.myspace.com/condimentsandwich"&gt;Condiment Sandwich&lt;/a&gt;. Woot!&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5783643-5128507873901306369?l=www.droptrio.com%2Fblog' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.droptrio.com/blog/2009/04/may-1-avantgarden.html</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Ian Varley)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5783643.post-919558772519103262</guid><pubDate>Sat, 28 Feb 2009 18:39:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-02-28T12:45:46.136-06:00</atom:updated><title>Thanks Fort Worth</title><description>Thanks to all our old friends that came to The Fairmount and new friends that we met there.  &lt;a href="http://gravityfeedband.com/"&gt;Gravity Feed&lt;/a&gt; grooves and &lt;a href="http://www.myspace.com/shuttlelive"&gt;Shuttle&lt;/a&gt; makes some big, fat, awesome noise.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a onblur="try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}" href="http://www.droptrio.com/blog/uploaded_images/DT-FW-20090227-709005.png"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 320px; height: 216px;" src="http://www.droptrio.com/blog/uploaded_images/DT-FW-20090227-708995.png" border="0" alt="" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5783643-919558772519103262?l=www.droptrio.com%2Fblog' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.droptrio.com/blog/2009/02/thanks-fort-worth.html</link><author>gerald.patrick.flanagan@gmail.com (Patrick Flanagan)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5783643.post-4943179496585863516</guid><pubDate>Sun, 22 Feb 2009 21:53:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-02-22T16:06:23.206-06:00</atom:updated><title>Ft. Forth Show, Friday 2/27</title><description>Denizens of the greater Dallas / Ft. Worth area with an interest in spaceship jazz: join us at &lt;a href="http://thefairmountlive.com/"&gt;The Fairmount&lt;/a&gt; on Friday, Feb. 27. &lt;a href="http://www.myspace.com/shuttlelive"&gt;Shuttle&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="http://www.myspace.com/gravityfeed"&gt;Gravity Feed&lt;/a&gt; will play as well. Hope to see you there!&lt;span style="font-style:italic;"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a onblur="try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}" href="http://www.droptrio.com/blog/uploaded_images/dt.fairmount.2009-02-27.small-741565.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="display:block; margin:0px auto 10px; text-align:center;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 278px; height: 400px;" src="http://www.droptrio.com/blog/uploaded_images/dt.fairmount.2009-02-27.small-741562.jpg" border="0" alt="" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5783643-4943179496585863516?l=www.droptrio.com%2Fblog' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.droptrio.com/blog/2009/02/ft-forth-show-friday-227.html</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (Ian Varley)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5783643.post-1898449070048215762</guid><pubDate>Sat, 24 Jan 2009 15:54:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-02-08T18:06:27.851-06:00</atom:updated><title>Pro Music Instruction</title><description>&lt;a onblur="try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}" href="http://www.droptrio.com/blog/uploaded_images/pmi-logo3-705387.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="float:left; margin:0 10px 10px 0;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 154px; height: 200px;" src="http://www.droptrio.com/blog/uploaded_images/pmi-logo3-705382.jpg" border="0" alt="" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Hey everyone, recently I opened a music school in the Woodlands, Texas called &lt;a href="http://www.pmiwoodlands.com"&gt;Pro Music Instruction&lt;/a&gt; with &lt;a href="http://www.rustycooley.com"&gt;Rusty Cooley&lt;/a&gt; and Larry Asher. All of us have been teaching in the Spring/Woodlands/Conroe area for over a decade.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are in need of a couple reliable, experienced (full time or part time) instructors. Our room rent is very affordable.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Contact us at info@pmiwoodlands.com.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;If you or your kids want to learn to play music, the school offers lessons for all ages and abilities:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Guitar (shred, rock, classical)&lt;br /&gt;Drums (metal, rock, jazz, funk)&lt;br /&gt;Piano (beginner)&lt;br /&gt;Electric &amp; upright bass (rock, jazz)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Thanks,&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.nujemusic.com"&gt;Nuje&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5783643-1898449070048215762?l=www.droptrio.com%2Fblog' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.droptrio.com/blog/2009/01/pro-music-instruction.html</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (nuje)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5783643.post-1062503780098213273</guid><pubDate>Sun, 18 Jan 2009 15:13:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-01-18T09:26:21.202-06:00</atom:updated><title>Drop Trio on Facebook</title><description>Although Facebook has its &lt;a href="http://www.thefuturebuzz.com/2008/04/14/myspace-and-facebook-%E2%80%93-the-modern-aol-and-prodigy/"&gt;short&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="http://aclu.org/pizza/"&gt;comings&lt;/a&gt;, you can now keep up with Drop Trio and listen to our music via our &lt;a href="http://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=1269862231&amp;ref=ts#/pages/Drop-Trio/48955782186?ref=s"&gt;Facebook group&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5783643-1062503780098213273?l=www.droptrio.com%2Fblog' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.droptrio.com/blog/2009/01/drop-trio-on-facebook.html</link><author>gerald.patrick.flanagan@gmail.com (Patrick Flanagan)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5783643.post-8377462838982375579</guid><pubDate>Tue, 30 Dec 2008 21:54:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2009-01-04T17:47:33.066-06:00</atom:updated><title>Houston Show in Early '09</title><description>&lt;a onblur="try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}" href="http://www.droptrio.com/blog/uploaded_images/dt.avantgarden.2009-01-30-794913.jpg"&gt;&lt;img style="float:left; margin:0 10px 10px 0;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;width: 223px; height: 320px;" src="http://www.droptrio.com/blog/uploaded_images/dt.avantgarden.2009-01-30-794908.jpg" border="0" alt="" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Happy New Year!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We have an upcoming show at our favorite Houston venue:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Friday, January 30&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.avantgardenhouston.com/"&gt;Avant Garden&lt;/a&gt; (411 Westheimer)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;More details to come.&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5783643-8377462838982375579?l=www.droptrio.com%2Fblog' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><link>http://www.droptrio.com/blog/2008/12/happy-new-year-we-have-upcoming-show-at.html</link><author>noreply@blogger.com (nuje)</author></item><item><guid isPermaLink='false'>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5783643.post-4919653955837589851</guid><pubDate>Thu, 12 Jun 2008 14:22:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:updated>2008-06-12T09:32:47.010-05:00</atom:updated><title>Escalator Music</title><description>Recently, we spent the day at &lt;a href="http://www.sugarhillstudios.com/"&gt;Sugarhill Studios&lt;/a&gt; tracking songs for a new album. We're hopeful for a 2008 release.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.droptrio.com/blog/uploaded_images/bass-717687.JPG"&gt;&lt;img style="float:left; margin:0 10px 10px 0;cursor:pointer; cursor:hand;" src="http://www.droptrio.com/blog/uploaded_images/bass-717069.JPG" border="0" alt="" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.droptrio.com/blog/uploaded_images/keys-718406.JPG"&gt;&lt;img style="float:left; margin:0 10px 10px 0;cursor:pointer; curso